{"tid":1431309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益！一人一個撚狗方法","createTime":"2019-08-08T03:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:17:26.000Z","uid":301362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e172db56e52c8275b5e9b6606ff26858d4593b","tid":1431309,"uid":301362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:17:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果</span><br />\n唔搞得屋企人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔打佢哋既話（還手唔計）<br />\n咁仲有啲咩方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真依家鬧佢哋個方法都進化左幾次：黑警/香港警察知法犯法-&gt;黑社會-&gt;用返佢哋啲宣誓挑起佢哋內心矛盾<br />\n不過佢哋有個好強既盾就係&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有權力</span><br />\n佢哋個邊個preach係：我地變撚左左害蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢哋係為民請命<br />\n當<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撚左自己係英雄</span></span><br />\n但大家有眼見，啲街坊幾乎全部都係屌9緊佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩辦法可以破撚左佢哋個盾，令佢哋徹底崩潰面對唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攞鏡逼佢哋望鳩返自己個閪樣好似ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.commondreams.org/sites/default/files/styles/cd_large/public/headlines/oakland.jpg?itok=UpltrkPz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commondreams.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fcd_large%2Fpublic%2Fheadlines%2Foakland.jpg%3Fitok%3DUpltrkPz&h=1d342a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource：<a href=\"https://www.commondreams.org/news/2014/08/22/oakland-protesters-hold-mirrors-police-officers-ferguson-solidarity-march\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.commondreams.org%2Fnews%2F2014%2F08%2F22%2Foakland-protesters-hold-mirrors-police-officers-ferguson-solidarity-march&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rNkum%2F%2B3HP0Ta45uqRfUpIg%3D&h=1d9468fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.commondreams.org/news/2014/08/22/oakland-protesters-hold-mirrors-police-officers-ferguson-solidarity-march</a>"}]}